{"tid":2489821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃臨福企圖縱火及管有汽油彈罪成 繼續還押候判 控方撤銷控告不依期歸押","createTime":"2021-04-15T07:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T08:23:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1c5d01b9a43de8e179efa9bb6c86b708259fdcdd","tid":2489821,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:44:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15060&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=0dced2c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15060</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第廿七庭<br />\n#李慶年法官 <br />\n#聆取對控罪的回答<br />\n#1014旺角 (原案A1)<br />\n<br />\n黃(16)🛑已還押逾3個月<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：有意圖而企圖縱火<br />\n被告被控於2019年10月14日，在旺角警署外連同A2和其他人有意圖而企圖用火摧毁或損壞旺角警署的側門，藉此危害他人生命，或罔顧他人生命是否會因而受危害。<br />\n<br />\n控罪2：管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產<br />\n被告被控於2019年10月14日，在其住所內管有用啤酒瓶製成的三個汽油彈，意圖使用或准許他人用以摧毀或損壞屬於另一人的財產；或以摧毀或損壞該人本人或使用人的財產，而且知道所用方法相當可能會危害另一人的生命。<br />\n<br />\n控罪3：沒有合理因由而沒有按照法庭的指定歸押<br />\n被告被控2020年4月27日，身為獲准保釋的人，無合理因由而沒有按照法庭的指定歸押。<br />\n<br />\n修改控罪：<br />\n控方移除控罪(3)<br />\n<br />\n被告對首2項控罪認罪‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n案件押後2021年7月6日 0930 灣仔區域法院進行答辯及求情，被告沒有保釋申請，期間繼續還押懲教看管🛑<br />\n<br />\n(按：黃手足不時望向旁聽席）"},{"pid":"2c698cf88055b8d68871ce43730def4332ab1aea","tid":2489821,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a243959833de6efb386f839b2386f87c0ad81df7","tid":2489821,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faea8f99b9a1b20a0552ec1cca394aa18b81d4af","tid":2489821,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9addf5d0534316b80ef330e1f8928250409ca4","tid":2489821,"uid":90282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:49:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">區院高院唔夠人啊</span>"},{"pid":"c98ea9441f336bf97fbe929361cdbc2b4bfff3f7","tid":2489821,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a16d2ae6519335839f844d0770796b597f9f7cc","tid":2489821,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db9addf5d0534316b80ef330e1f8928250409ca4","tid":2489821,"uid":90282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:49:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">區院高院唔夠人啊</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6661fb12be1005c161739e253d31d088b520b4","tid":2489821,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"點解會移除罪三既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49e85019e3f937a0fcaed8d402180cdd2355101","tid":2489821,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b6661fb12be1005c161739e253d31d088b520b4","tid":2489821,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:22:57.0